text.tspan: Based on the expert estimates and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to
which women are represented in the legislature and have an equal share of political power. It ranges from 0 to 1
Note: The score in recent years is very high even though many countries are far from equal participation because the index scores them
relative to the historical average across countries.
